次数以及是否被锁定。 不知道知乎各位大佬有没有更好的解决方案，各位有什么好的解决办法吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IpMjopb20/t9uEAMaCTEwOTQ2OTQxNCD0h/20BjAAOF1AEnIJNjYyMzYyNDc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"83 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8405179db9e611897742050eb05edc96_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1721971088.495688","card_id":"Q_661209333","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":661209333,"title":"如何评价乌尔善执导，胡先煦、李宛妲、冯绍峰主演的奇幻电影《异人之下》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661209333","type":"question","created":1720572014,"answer_count":17,"follower_count":21,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[199834,230067,1631937,3144656,3498261],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IpMjopb20/t9uEAMaCTEwOTIxMjk5OSDusLe0BjAAOBVAE3IJNjYxMjA5MzMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"74 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8259f9bc693d6a374363592b1e61253a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1721971088.495981","card_id":"Q_662548655","target":{"id":662548655,"title":"每天让你坚持上班的理由是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662548655","type":"question","created":1721890127,"answer_count":86,"follower_count":98,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[8542,9469,9671,11486,12585],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IpMjopb20/t9uEAMaCTEwOTUxMDg0MCDP6oe1BjAAOGJAFHIJNjYyNTQ4NjU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"74